The paper discusses the deployment of AI-based services on mobile devices, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper proposes a method for bit allocation in collaborative intelligence, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with deep neural networks, which are commonly used in multimedia applications (cs.MM). Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which are commonly used in neural networks (cs.NE).
